(12149, 1, '2015-09-04 06:45:18', '2015-09-04 06:45:18', '[spb_single_image image="12151" image_size="full" frame="noframe" intro_animation="none" full_width="no" lightbox="no" link_target="_self" el_class="sch-img" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [fullwidth_text alt_background="none" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Solid Step International School provides a safe and secure environment for the secondary school students. We take students with special interests, abilities and talents and motivates them to expand and develop in a learning environment enhanced with enthusiastic teachers and peers.We encourage everyone to join in a wide range of activities, to discover their talents and grow in self-confidence and self-knowledge. We also try to develop skills of leadership, fellowship and service both for individual benefit and for the overall strength of the community of which our studentsn are an essential part</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Solid Step International School strives to provide a broad range of academic, social, and cultural experiences that will prepare our students to be successful in universities and to become contributing members of a global society. Through having a fully graduate staff, several with higher degrees and with nearly all staff having many years of teaching experience. This allows us to understand and react positively and appropriately to practical problems or difficulties the student might encounter, both academic and otherwise.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We want students to develop their individuality and we must identify their talents in an environment where they feel safe and valued. Ours is a diverse, down-to-earth school which thrives on curiosity, challenge, encouragement and kindness; where everyone listens and responds to each other. It is our shared sense of belonging which gives our school its energy, its collective strength, its rigour and its ability to inspire pupils to excel. Excellent teaching in a disciplined environment is at the heart of the School.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We very much value parental interest, co-operation and support. We aim to be approachable. Through our unique tutor system, we aim to develop productive links between home and school. We aim to be a supportive, caring and friendly community with the promotion of self-discipline, reflection, social responsibility and integrity at the heart of all that we do.</p>\r\n[/fullwidth_text]', 'Secondary School', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'secondary-school', '', '', '2015-09-04 06:45:18', '2015-09-04 06:45:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/mine/SolidSteps/?p=12149', 0, 'post', '', 0),
