nt, effort and behaviour from all our pupils/students. We maximize student attainment, provide support, welfare and inspiration in a secure and healthy environment, committed to continuous improvement. Our students will be confident, successful and able to contribute effectively and responsibly to society. Our school''s motto ''Taking Solid Steps into academic success with the home zone advantage'' stems from our belief that success can only come through a close partnership between dedicated staff, confident students, supportive parents and a committed Management Team. We look forward to working with you to enable your child to achieve their full potential.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">We are proud of our record of building positive relationships between students, and between staff and students. We always seek to share our values with all members of the school and the wider community. Involving students families in monitoring and promoting progress is a vital part of what we do, and we are always looking for new and better ways to communicate, because we know that when student, school and family work together, we can create the power to drive achievement.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: -4px;">Mrs Okpor, J.I.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style="color: #3465aa;">Proprietress and Director of Studies</h4>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row] [testimonial_slider title="Testimonials" text_size="large" item_count="6" order="date" category="home" autoplay="yes" alt_background="alt-three" el_class="mt0 mb0 bb0 bt0 testi-space" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-13 04:14:47', '2015-09-13 04:14:47', '', 2, 'http://localhost/mine/SolidSteps/2015/09/13/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
