ight" bg_type="cover" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" parallax_video_height="window-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" row_overlay_opacity="0" row_padding_vertical="65" row_padding_horizontal="4" row_margin_vertical="0" remove_element_spacing="no" inner_column_height="col-natural" row_el_class="row-color" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_icon_box title="SCHOOL MOTTO" box_type="standard" character="A" color="accent" target="_self" animation="none" animation_delay="0" width="1/3" el_position="first"]\r\n\r\n<strong style="color: #000; font-size: 16px;">Taking Solid Steps into academic success with the home zone advantage.</strong>\r\n\r\n[/spb_icon_box] [spb_icon_box title="MISSION STATEMENT" box_type="standard" character="B" color="accent" target="_self" animation="none" animation_delay="0" width="1/3"]\r\n\r\n<strong style="color: #000; font-size: 16px;">To assert that academic excellence and glory can be achieved without malpractice.</strong>\r\n\r\n[/spb_icon_box] [spb_icon_box title="OUR VISION" box_type="standard" character="C" color="accent" target="_self" animation="none" animation_delay="0" width="1/3" el_position="last"]\r\n\r\n<strong style="color: #000; font-size: 16px;">To raise leaders and champions that would create positive and noticeable difference in the society.</strong>\r\n\r\n[/spb_icon_box] [/spb_row] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_text_block title="OUR SCHOOL CHARACTER &amp; UNIFORMS" pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/2" el_position="first"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The uniform reflects the school character and greatly contributes to a childs sense of belonging and pride in their school. The school colors are navy blue and white. Solid Steps international schools pinafores, shorts, shirts, blouses, polo shirts, cardigans, books and bags all bearing the schools branding are on sale at the school offices</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Please note that nail varnish, make up, colored hair, hair beads and bold jewellery are deemed inappropriate for school. All clothing, bags, pencil cases, flasks and bottles must be clearly named. Mobile phones, iPods, computer games, toys etc. shall not be permitted in school.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block title="HEALTH &amp; SAFETY" pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/2" el_position="last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We want to be known as a healthy school and we encourage healthy lifestyles and healthy eating. We have facilities to provide healthy and balanced diets for the children and we encourage parents if they wish to pack lunches for their children to ensure healthy diets too.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">At Solid Steps, we ensure that all adults working at the school are committed to safeguarding our children, we observe safety measures at all times</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">First aid boxes are available at the school with trained staff to administer . Specific teachers and teaching assistants are trained to administer first aid treatments, if and when required.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block title="OUR SCHOOL PLEDGE" pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/2" el_position="first"]\r\n\r\n<dl class="ic-txt"><dt>I pledge to Solid Steps my school\r\nTo be diligent, obedient and honest\r\nTo study well to be a leader and champion\r\nTo serve as a shinning example to my peers\r\nTo assert that academic excellence can be achieved without malpractice\r\nAnd create positive difference in the society\r\nSo help me God</dt><dd></dd></dl>[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block title="OUR SCHOOL ANTHEM" pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/2" el_position="last"]\r\n\r\n<dl class="ic-txt"><dt>Solid Steps\r\nAn academy established by vision from God\r\nWhere the Leaders and Champions are raised\r\nTo lead while others follow\r\nTo command while others obey</dt></dl><dl class="ic-txt"><dt>We shall rule\r\nWe shall lead\r\nWe shall excel\r\nWhere others fail</dt></dl>[/spb_text_block]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12023-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-13 05:20:24', '2015-09-13 05:20:24', '', 12023, 'http://localhost/mine/SolidSteps/2015/09/13/12023-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(12221, 1, '2015-09-13 05:38:01', '2015-09-13 05:38:01', '[fullwidth_text alt_background="none" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<p class="head1" style="text-align: center;">Statement of Solid Steps International Schools Ethos</p>\r\n<p class="parag" style="text-align: center;">Our philosophy at Solid Steps International School is simple. Provide a secure, purposeful environment, deliver first class teaching that inspires and challenges and celebrate each child for who they are and what they do.</p>\r\n[/fullwidth_text] [boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#474479" custom_text_colour="#000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">We are a forward-thinking school aiming to prepare our children and students for a rapidly changing world by equipping them with critical thinking skills, global perspective, and respect for core values of honesty, loyalty, and compassion. Developing these skills is the corner stone of the education we offer.Students will have success for today and be prepared for tomorrow.</p>\r\n[/boxed_content] [fullwidth_text title="SOLID STEPS INTERNATIONAL SCHOOL''S AIMS" alt_background="none" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<h3 class="aim-color">Teaching and Learning</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To provide excellence and learning across all subjects.</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">Inspirational Staff who celebrates each child for their individuality and achievements.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="aim-color">Standards and Expectations</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To motivate through a challenging environment that fosters creativity, curiosity and confidence.</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">By setting high expectations for each and every boy and girl tracking their progress to ensure to ensure they gain the highest qualification alongside a wealth of other skills.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="aim-color">Self-Development and Adaptability</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To encourage boys and girls to be resilient, flexible and adaptable by providing them with situations that develop their capacity to respond in novel situations.</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To encourage staff with the desire to reflect on their practice, learn new skills, show innovation and be adaptable to change.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="aim-color">Communication</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To inspire our boys and girls in acquiring the art, skills and confidence to communicate with clarity with both spoken and written word.</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To inspire a community in which everyone is respectful of others and understands how to communicate appropriately; in particular social media.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="aim-color">The Business of Education</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To instil in our boys and girls an appreciation that a significant investment has been made in their education by both parents and school; and tat with privilege comes responsibility.</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To instil a sense of commitment in our boys,girls and staff to promote their school a s ambassadors to ensure its continued success as a school which offers and excellent education for young people and an excellent working environment for staff..</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fullwidth_text]', 'Aims and Ethos', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12079-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-13 05:38:01', '2015-09-13 05:38:01', '', 12079, 'http://localhost/mine/SolidSteps/2015/09/13/12079-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(12222, 1, '2015-09-13 05:39:00', '2015-09-13 05:39:00', '[fullwidth_text alt_background="none" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<p class="head1" style="text-align: center;">Statement of Solid Steps International Schools Ethos</p>\r\n<p class="parag" style="text-align: center;">Our philosophy at Solid Steps International School is simple. Provide a secure, purposeful environment, deliver first class teaching that inspires and challenges and celebrate each child for who they are and what they do.</p>\r\n[/fullwidth_text] [boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#faebd7" custom_text_colour="#000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">We are a forward-thinking school aiming to prepare our children and students for a rapidly changing world by equipping them with critical thinking skills, global perspective, and respect for core values of honesty, loyalty, and compassion. Developing these skills is the corner stone of the education we offer.Students will have success for today and be prepared for tomorrow.</p>\r\n[/boxed_content] [fullwidth_text title="SOLID STEPS INTERNATIONAL SCHOOL''S AIMS" alt_background="none" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<h3 class="aim-color">Teaching and Learning</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To provide excellence and learning across all subjects.</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">Inspirational Staff who celebrates each child for their individuality and achievements.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="aim-color">Standards and Expectations</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To motivate through a challenging environment that fosters creativity, curiosity and confidence.</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">By setting high expectations for each and every boy and girl tracking their progress to ensure to ensure they gain the highest qualification alongside a wealth of other skills.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="aim-color">Self-Development and Adaptability</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To encourage boys and girls to be resilient, flexible and adaptable by providing them with situations that develop their capacity to respond in novel situations.</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To encourage staff with the desire to reflect on their practice, learn new skills, show innovation and be adaptable to change.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="aim-color">Communication</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To inspire our boys and girls in acquiring the art, skills and confidence to communicate with clarity with both spoken and written word.</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To inspire a community in which everyone is respectful of others and understands how to communicate appropriately; in particular social media.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="aim-color">The Business of Education</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To instil in our boys and girls an appreciation that a significant investment has been made in their education by both parents and school; and tat with privilege comes responsibility.</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">To instil a sense of commitment in our boys,girls and staff to promote their school a s ambassadors to ensure its continued success as a school which offers and excellent education for young people and an excellent working environment for staff..</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fullwidth_text]', 'Aims and Ethos', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12079-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-13 05:39:00', '2015-09-13 05:39:00', '', 12079, 'http://localhost/mine/SolidSteps/2015/09/13/12079-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(12223, 1, '2015-09-13 05:46:58', '2015-09-13 05:46:58', '[spb_single_image image="12191" image_size="full" frame="noframe" intro_animation="none" full_width="no" lightbox="no" link_target="_self" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [fullwidth_text alt_background="none" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<h2 style="color: #292b47;">Little Feet Big Steps</h2>\r\n<blockquote style="padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0 0 20px; border-left: 5px solid #474479;">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 18px;">Striving to make your child feel happy and safe as they take their first steps into our School community.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Sold Steps International Creche and Nursery School, provides strong foundations for your childs future success. It strives to develop the talents, skills and enthusiasm for learning that will help your child thrive through this important, formative time, senior school years and into adult life. Here, with us, children quickly become part of a community of learners, where each individual is unique. We help them to challenge themselves to develop their skills and talents throughout their learning journey.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our teaching in the Nursery School and Creche is based on the Early Years Foundation Stage Curriculum and there is a strong emphasis on exploration, investigation discovery and problem solving.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Throughout Solid Steps International School we celebrate the individuality of our boys and girls. Children flourish in an environment where they can be themselves and we proactively look for hidden talents, providing a more rounded holistic education.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We aim for children to leave our Foundation Stage as happy, confident, independent and resourceful learners who have a thirst for knowledge and are eager to embrace new challenges.</p>\r\n[/fullwidth_text]', 'Creche and Nursery', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12190-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-13 05:46:58', '2015-09-13 05:46:58', '', 12190, 'http://localhost/mine/SolidSteps/2015/09/13/12190-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(12224, 1, '2015-09-13 05:52:20', '2015-09-13 05:52:20', '<p style="text-align: justify;">We can never presume to know just how difficult it must be for you to choose or change your childs school, but we strive to be on hand throughout the admissions process to answer any questions you have and make the enrolment of your child as simple and as straightforward as possible. A single point of contact from initial enquiry through to enrolment ensures that you receive expert personal attention from a member of our experienced team at all times.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="aim-color">The following are the steps to follow</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Get the application form from the school Admin Office.</li>\r\n	<li>Kindly complete the application form which is then returned with a recent passport, copies of birth certificates, immunization records and school reports for the last two years, if appropriate.</li>\r\n	<li>Make an appointment for interview/assessment.</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;">All applications are then carefully reviewed by our Senior Management Team. All new families are, of course, invited to visit us prior to starting school. Experience has shown that the correct placement of children ensures a smoother and happier adaptation and integration, as a result children joining the school from Year 4 onwards are asked to complete a short assessment to assist us in placing them in the most suitable class.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">If you have any further questions then please call the school on the following numbers; 08056407790, 08028834187, 07037746048, 08161730788 or by email to solidstepsch@yahoo.com</p>', 'Admission', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12176-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-13 05:52:20', '2015-09-13 05:52:20', '', 12176, 'http://localhost/mine/SolidSteps/12176-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(12225, 1, '2015-09-13 05:53:40', '2015-09-13 05:53:40', '[sf_gallery gallery_id="12167" slider_transition="slide" show_thumbs="yes" autoplay="yes" show_captions="yes" enable_lightbox="yes" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [fullwidth_text alt_background="none" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<h3 class="aim-color" style="text-align: justify;">Our facilities are not just modern and sophisticated but function in all respects. Among others, our facilities include the following:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">First class facilities and teaching aids</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">Spacious and air-conditioned classrooms.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">One teacher to 12 pupils/students ratio to ensure close monitory.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">Executive fleet of air-conditioned school buses.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">Computer/ICT laboratory with internet facilities.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">Well stocked library.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">Experienced and seasoned teachers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">Air-conditioned multi-purpose school hall.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">Installed CCTV for effective supervision, check and resolution.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">Spacious and carpet grass playing ground with modern gadgets.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">24 hours security by trained security operatives.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">Continuous re-investment in human and material resources.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">Well equipped laboratories for various subjects and trades.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">Well equipped Health Embassy (Sick Bay) manned by registered, experience and qualified nurses.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">50KV super sound/noise proof power generator .</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fullwidth_text]', 'Facilities', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12164-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-13 05:53:40', '2015-09-13 05:53:40', '', 12164, 'http://localhost/mine/SolidSteps/12164-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(12226, 1, '2015-09-13 05:57:14', '2015-09-13 05:57:14', '[spb_gmaps address="7-9 Williams Bademosi Street, Off Governor Road, Emmanuel Bus Stop, Ikotun, Lagos Nigeria" size="400" type="ROADMAP" zoom="14" saturation="color" fullscreen="yes" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [blank_spacer height="20px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [fullwidth_text alt_background="none" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<p class="head1" style="text-align: center;">We need your Feedback</p>\r\n<p class="parag" style="text-align: center;">We are passionate about building a world class school, raising the bar in education by providing the best facilities and teachers, guiding each child to find purpose at an early age and express himself or herself without fear or a sense of limitation.</p>\r\n[/fullwidth_text] [spb_row wrap_type="content-width" row_bg_type="color" color_row_height="content-height" bg_type="cover" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" parallax_video_height="window-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" row_overlay_opacity="0" row_padding_vertical="65" row_padding_horizontal="4" row_margin_vertical="0" remove_element_spacing="no" inner_column_height="col-natural" row_el_class="row-color" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_text_block title="IF YOU HAVE ANY CONCERNS" pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/2" el_position="first"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Please do not hesitate to contact the any of school''s teachers who will be very happy to address any concerns you may have. In the event that you are not satisfied please book an appointment to see the schools director proprietress Mrs Okpor, J.I at the school office</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block title="IF WE HAVE ANY CONCERNS" pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/2" el_position="last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">If we have any concerns about your childs development or behaviour, w